  <description>
    <p>A fully reverse engineered PC port of the the 90s action RPG.</p>
    <p><em>PLEASE NOTE:</em> This Flatpak does <em>not</em> include any game data.
        Please copy at least the files <code>Htic2-0.pak</code> and <code>Htic2-1.pak</code>
        <code>$HOME/.var/app/io.github.m0rb.heretic2r/heretic2r/base/</code>.</p>
    <p>Launching the game will inform you with a message if any of the required
        files are missing and where you need to copy them.</p>
  </description>
